OL,3,CArtificial pancreas to be given to
OL,4,Cwomen with diabetes to cut pregnancy
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FPregnant women in England with type 1
OL,8,Fdiabetes are set to be given a special
OL,9,Fartificial pancreas to reduce the risk
OL,10,Fof stillbirth and miscarriage.
OL,12,FMothers-to-be with the condition have
OL,13,Fhigher risks, as pregnancy hormones
OL,14,Fcan make it harder for them to
OL,15,Fregulate their blood glucose levels.
OL,17,FDuring pregnancy, poorly controlled
OL,18,Fdiabetes can increase the risk of
OL,19,Fstillbirth, miscarriage, larger
OL,20,Fbabies, birth injuries, and the need
OL,21,Ffor neonatal care.
