OL,3,CArtificial pancreas to be given to
OL,4,Cwomen with diabetes to cut pregnancy
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FThe new tool, also known as a hybrid
OL,8,Fclosed-loop system, will be offered to
OL,9,Fthe 2,000 women with type 1 diabetes
OL,10,Fwho become pregnant each year.
OL,12,FIt will also be offered to women who
OL,13,Fhave type 1 diabetes and are planning
OL,14,Fa pregnancy, NHS England said.
OL,16,FThe technology, which is linked to a
OL,17,Fmobile phone app, delivers the precise
OL,18,Finsulin dosage a woman requires before
OL,19,Fand during pregnancy.
OL,21,FWhat is type 1 diabetes?
