OL,3,CArtificial pancreas to be given to
OL,4,Cwomen with diabetes to cut pregnancy
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FUnlike other artificial pancreases,
OL,8,Fthis allows pregnant women to set a
OL,9,Fglucose target to the lower level
OL,10,Frequired to achieve better outcomes in
OL,11,Fpregnancy, NHS England said.
OL,13,FIt also allows remote monitoring by
OL,14,Fhealth workers, meaning fewer check-
OL,15,Fups for mothers-to-be.
OL,17,FThe tool has already been used by
OL,18,Fseveral women, including mother-of-two
OL,19,FNina Willer, 40, a diabetes specialist
OL,20,Fmidwife at Norfolk and Norwich
OL,21,FUniversity Hospital.
