OL,3,CArtificial pancreas to be given to
OL,4,Cwomen with diabetes to cut pregnancy
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,F"This new generation 'artificial
OL,8,Fpancreas' is a game-changer for women
OL,9,Fwith type 1 diabetes who are pregnant
OL,10,For planning a pregnancy, so it is
OL,11,Ffantastic that its available on NHS to
OL,12,Fprotect the health of mums-to-be and
OL,13,Fbabies," Ms Willer said.
OL,15,F"As someone who has used this tech
OL,16,Fwhen I was pregnant with my own
OL,17,Fdaughter, and as an NHS diabetes
OL,18,Fspecialist midwife to help my patients.
